<li><a href="#orgcc6a2c6"><span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> 50. Application of recombinant DNA technologies in medicine. DNA polymorphisms. Detection of mutations by allele-specific probes and by PCR. Detection of a variable number of tandem repeats. Genetic counselling. Production of vaccines and therapeutic proteins. Gene therapy. Cases in forensic medicine. Transgenic animals. DNA chips in diagnostics.</a></li>
